column1: ### Level-3 GRACE/GRACE-FO M-SSA solution of surface mass density anomalies, expressed in Equivalent Water Height (EWH)
# Solution processed following the method proposed by Gauer et al. , in revision for Journal of Geophysical Research - Solid Earth, 2023
# Combined solution computed using Level-2 GRACE/GRACE-FO gravity fields provided by the CSR, GFZ, ITSG TU-GRAZ and JPL processing centers
# Stokes coefficients C1.0, C1.1 and S1.1 have been added following TN-13
# Stokes coefficient C2.0 has been replaced following TN-14
# Stokes coefficient C3.0 has been replaced following TN-14  for the 2012-03 to 2022-09 period
